metadata.name: AdoraDoggo - Olive
metadata.description:
AdoraDoggo is here! Meet Olive the Shih Tzu! Olive loves naps and yummy food. She can be a sassy pup, but her kindness shines bright. Not to mention, she is one stylish girl!

Olive is the first animated drop from artist Agnes Garbowska.

I create art to bring smiles and joy. I enjoy working with cute characters and calming colours. I hope this piece makes you smile since creating it made me happy and I learned a lot during the process.
